      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic refinement. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and performance. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning buyer. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber, pre-owned vehicle that maintains an impressive balance of quality and value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really wonderful shape. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and has plenty of life left for its next owner. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of use as you\u2019d expect, but it\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a champ! I\u2019m happy to chat or answer any questions you have\u2014I really want this to go to a great home. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus, paired to a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The engine is mechanically sound, benefiting from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a high-flow water pump to ensure thermal management. The chassis remains composed under lateral load thanks to a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers and factory-spec bushings. While the exterior shows the honest patina of an enjoyed enthusiast car, the drivetrain is dialed in, delivering linear power delivery and the communicative steering feedback synonymous with the 911 platform. Recent service includes a full fluid flush and a new clutch assembly, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor exterior wear. Engine runs smooth. Interior is clean.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and refined comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish that catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment. The premium leather upholstery remains supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the high-fidelity sound system, navigation, and heated seats\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with recent records showing a fresh oil service and a brake pad replacement. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. While it possesses the natural character of a pre-owned vehicle, its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal make it a standout choice. Full service history is available upon request.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has been rigorously maintained, ensuring a dependable driving experience for its next proprietor. Offering a harmonious balance of performance and value, this selection represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show you around!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
