      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and retains its signature individual throttle body induction system. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative measures have been completed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS unit refresh to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-tuned damping. While the finish displays honest road patina, the drivetrain and structural components are dialed in for the purist driver. No deferred maintenance or hydraulic leaks.",
